The '''Cardiff Big Weekend''' took place annually from 1993 to 2011 as part of the Cardiff Festival organised by [[Cardiff Council]].{{cn|date=September 2018}} It lasted three days and was billed as "the UK’s biggest free outdoor music festival".{{cn|date=September 2018}}
Among the acts at the Pride Cymru Big Weekend in 2017 were [[Bright Light Bright Light]], [[Charlotte Church]] and [[Zervas & Pepper]].<ref name=walesonline2017>Kathryn Williams, [http://www.walesonline.co.uk/whats-on/music-nightlife-news/line-up-years-pride-cymru-13027616 This is the line up for this year's Pride Cymru Big Weekend event in Cardiff], [[Wales Online]], 12 May 2017, Accessed 19 July 2017</ref>
